---
import CallToAction from '~/components/widgets/CallToAction.astro';
import Content from '~/components/widgets/Content.astro';
import Features3 from '~/components/widgets/Features3.astro';
import Hero from '~/components/widgets/Hero.astro';
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useRoutes } from '~/utils/i18n';

const u = useRoutes(getLangFromUrl(Astro.url));

const metadata = {
  title: 'Bootstrap Programming Company',
  description: `With Bootstrap, we create responsive user interfaces (Frontend), adapted to mobile, tablet, and computer. We carry out custom layout and design. Free quote!`,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <Hero
    tagline="A single code, multiple presentation formats."
    actions={[{ variant: 'primary', text: 'Free Quote', href: u('contact') }]}
    backgroundImage={{ alt: 'Abstract background', src: '~/assets/images/geometric-2/4.jpg' }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="title">
      Responsive interface development with <span class="text-accent highlight">Bootstrap</span>
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      We have a team of expert Bootstrap programmers, ready to develop professional tools with this framework.
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <Content
    classes={{ container: 'contains-logo pb-0 md:pb-0 lg:pb-0' }}
    isImageSmall
    title="<span class='custom-gradient'>Bootstrap: </span> We design modern and adaptable interfaces"
    image={{
      id: 'bootstrap-logo',
      src: '~/assets/images/tecnologia/bootstrap-logo.svg',
      alt: 'Bootstrap Logo - Framework for responsive interfaces',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <p class="text-muted">
        At Gilsys, we use Bootstrap to build modern, responsive, and highly functional interfaces. As one of the most
        widely used CSS frameworks in the world, Bootstrap offers a solid and efficient solution for designing intuitive
        web applications that adapt to any device.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted mt-4">
        Its flexibility makes it ideal for dynamic frontends and backends with responsive layout, ensuring a fluid and
        accessible experience for all users.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted mt-4">
        <a title="Custom web application development" href={u('development/web')} class="btn-primary mt-12 mb-12 w-auto"
          >Explore our custom web development services</a
        >
      </p>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <Content
    title={`We create <span class="custom-gradient">responsive</span> user interfaces`}
    subtitle={`Adapted to mobile, tablet, and computer`}
    image={{
      src: '~/assets/images/tecnologia/bootstrap-responsive.png',
      alt: 'Scenario for Bootstrap - Responsive interfaces',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <p class="text-muted">
        Bootstrap offers a solid foundation for designing clean and professional interfaces without writing CSS code
        from scratch. Its flexible grid system, predefined components, and mobile-first approach allow us to speed up
        the development process without compromising customization.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted mt-4">
        <a title="Bootstrap official page" target="_blank" href="https://getbootstrap.com/" class="btn-primary mt-12 mb-12 w-auto"
          >Visit the official Bootstrap website</a
        >
      </p>
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-lightgray"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <Features3
    title="Benefits of using Bootstrap in your project"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Adaptable design on any screen',
        description: `Bootstrap ensures your interface looks good on any device without extra effort.`,
        icon: 'tabler:screen-share',
      },
      {
        title: 'Optimized structure for development',
        description: `Organizes information and content efficiently, facilitating layout and maintenance.`,
        icon: 'tabler:layout-grid',
      },
      {
        title: 'Production-ready components',
        description: `Includes buttons, forms, alerts, and more, reducing development time without sacrificing customization.`,
        icon: 'tabler:components',
      },
      {
        title: 'Flexible grid system',
        description: `Allows creating fluid and well-structured designs, dynamically adapting to each project's need.`,
        icon: 'tabler:squares-diagonal',
      },
      {
        title: 'Compatibility with all browsers',
        description: `Works smoothly on Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari, and others, ensuring a homogeneous user experience.`,
        icon: 'tabler:browser-check',
      },
      {
        title: 'Constantly evolving community and ecosystem',
        description: `Thousands of developers contribute with improvements, plugins, and solutions, making Bootstrap a solid and up-to-date option.`,
        icon: 'tabler:users-group',
      },
      {
        title: 'Advanced customization without effort',
        description: `Adjust styles, colors, and variables easily to make the design fit your project's identity.`,
        icon: 'tabler:settings',
      },
      {
        title: 'Speeds up development time',
        description: `Reduces the learning curve and launches projects faster with its built-in tools and utilities.`,
        icon: 'tabler:bolt',
      },
      {
        title: 'Detailed and accessible documentation',
        description: `Find practical examples and clear guides to implement any functionality without complications.`,
        icon: 'tabler:manual-gearbox',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <Content
    isImageSmall
    title="At Gilsys, we have trusted Bootstrap since its beginnings"
    subtitle="We have relied on this framework since its first versions, which gives us a deep understanding of its operation."
    image={{
      src: '~/assets/images/tecnologia/bootstrap-interfaz.png',
      alt: 'User interface and Bootstrap components',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <p class="text-muted">
        From Bootstrap version 3 to the current one, we have worked with this framework to develop efficient
        applications with attractive interfaces. Thanks to our experience, we can adapt it to projects of varying
        complexity, from corporate websites to interactive platforms and advanced back offices.
      </p>
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-lightgray"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <Content
    isReversed
    title="Maintenance and evolution with Bootstrap"
    image={{
      src: '~/assets/images/tecnologia/bootstrap-uiux.jpg',
      alt: 'Bootstrap UI UX image',
    }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Code optimization',
        description: 'Implying reduction of unnecessary styles.',
        icon: 'tabler:code',
      },
      {
        title: 'Adaptation of old interfaces to modern versions',
        description: 'Thanks to its regular updates, we can implement aesthetic and functional improvements.',
        icon: 'tabler:tool',
      },
      {
        title: 'Integration with other frameworks and web technologies.',
        description: 'As experts in custom development, we can integrate additional components or program them to measure.',
        icon: 'tabler:plug',
      },
    ]}
  >
    <Fragment slot="preContent">
      <p class="text-muted">
        At Gilsys, Bootstrap is not just a tool, it is part of our DNA. With years of experience and a deep passion for
        this framework, we create exceptional interfaces that combine functionality and cutting-edge design. We ensure
        that each interface not only stays updated and functional but also reflects the latest trends in web design.
      </p>
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="postContent">
      <p class="text-muted">
        At Gilsys, we ensure that each interface not only stays updated and functional but also reflects the latest
        trends in web design.
      </p>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <CallToAction
    backgroundImage={{ src: '~/assets/images/geometric-2/4.jpg', alt: 'Abstract background' }}
    actions={[
      {
        variant: 'primary',
        text: 'Free Quote',
        href: u('contact'),
      },
      {
        variant: 'primary',
      text: 'Call',
      href: 'tel:+34711239085',
    },
  ]}
>
  <Fragment slot="title">
    We are <span class="custom-gradient">Bootstrap specialists</span><br />Let us handle the layout
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="subtitle">
    We take care of the design, layout, and responsive adaptation of your project's user interface.
  </Fragment>
</CallToAction>
</Layout>